latestPosts.caption: Happy 10 to us 🥰 10 years of love, laughter, struggles, happy  and sad tears, highs and lows, we have seen it all in this one decade of togetherness. I am so proud of us for always believing in each other, for always supporting each other, for always keeping our chin high even when the chips were down. Most  importantly thank you for always guiding me, mentoring me . Love you 🥰cheers to us.i am  so ready to enter in this next decade with heart full of gratitude and the never ending spirit of learning. You are indeed one of a kind and I am lucky I got you .🥰🥰
